    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Concessio in <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">emphyteusim</rs> seu
                        renovatio unius <rs key="#Landed_possessions">spatii terrê</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Houses">domo</rs> positê <placeName
                            key="#Houses #Landed_possessions" ref="#places/594">Ravennê</placeName>
                        ad <rs key="#Roads">plateam publicam</rs> in regione <orgName>S.
                            Agathê</orgName> et ad <orgName>S. Mariam in Cartularia</orgName>, facta
                        a domina <persName><name ref="Gaurga">Gasberga</name></persName> filia
                            <persName key="#Marquis/duke"><name ref="Natalis"
                            >Natalis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">ducis</rs>, favore <persName><name
                                ref="Petrus/Comes">Petri vocatur Comitis</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Maria">Mariê</name></persName> uxoris eius et
                        filiorum. Actum Ravennê. Rog. <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Stephanus"
                                >Stephani</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs>. Anno domini <persName key="#Popes"
                            ref="#people/2137">Benedicti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">papê</rs> VI, <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/130">Henrici</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs> V, indictione II, 26
                        novembris.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>Mezzetti, <foreign>Le carte</foreign>, pp. 253-254, n° 113.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
